30
00:03:14,650 --> 00:03:20,350
Please let me confirm. You are The Unstoppable, K-san?

31
00:03:20,350 --> 00:03:22,200
Not K-san. It's Katsura.

32
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:26,590
No, but... you asked me to use an alias...

33
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:28,600
K-tsura-san.

34
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:30,450
It's not K-tsura-san. It's Katsura!

35
00:03:30,450 --> 00:03:34,480
Umm... Are you sure you want to give your real name?

36
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:36,690
